  "text": "The stage of development of an impacted permanent maxillary central incisor may also influence eruption of this tooth. Some reports suggest that incisors with immature roots are more likely to erupt spontaneously following supernumerary removal than those with mature roots. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] However, other studies have found no association between the eruption of unerupted maxillary incisors and their stage of root development. ",
